  "tldr_evidence": "Phase A design refresh needs a typography/palette token foundation before typography can be applied or palette restricted. This EXP adds Google Fonts (Source Serif 4, Inter, JetBrains Mono) and --serif/--sans/--mono plus semantic ink/rule/accent/warn/crit/good tokens to :root and its dark override — no existing selector changes, no visual shift yet.",
  "tldr_verdict": "DRAFT — foundational tokens only, no visual change, no consumer yet. Every one of the seven Phase A items that follows (typography application, stance statement, bar chart, accuracy-math demotion, Latest Findings demotion, palette restriction, a11y fixes) either consumes these tokens or coexists with them. Integration is blocked until the operator posts an approval HNOTE naming EXP-202."
